        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JM for his liberal offer [to publish <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>]. CD fears the public will not be interested, but thinks it will "do good to the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> as it will show that I worked hard on details and it will <hi rend="italic">perhaps</hi> serve [to] illustrate how Natural History may be worked under the belief of the modification of Species".</p> 
        </abstract>
